Quickpay,is,an,online,payment,solution,for,merchants,that,allows,the,secure,integration,of,credit,and,debit,cards,with,an,arbitrary,site,on,the,Internet,The,service,works,with,all,major,credit,cards,as,well,as,Paypal,Sofort,Banking,and,other,e,banking,facilities,The,QuickPay,API,enables,merchants,to,handle,payments,in,a,simple,manner,Based,on,SSL,encrypted,HTTP,communication,all,actions,are,performed,by,sending,a,HTTP,POST,request,Responses,are,sent,as,an,XML,document